Interface Settings

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.hibernate.cfg.AvailableSettings, org.hibernate.jpa.AvailableSettings
    public interface Settings
extends org.hibernate.cfg.AvailableSettings
    Configuration properties for the Hibernate Reactive persistence provider, for use with ReactiveServiceRegistryBuilder.
